ie spotka\u0142am si\u0119 z takim argumentem, ale masz racj\u0119, \u017ce na pewno zmienia to odbi\u00f3r firmy.","created_at":1547660288,"did_report_as_spam":false,"owner":{"id":"6944544886","is_verified":false,"profile_pic_url":"https://scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/05d0f27c5f82275615c717b1fc329879/5D463364/t51.2885-19/s150x150/53728884_2268498406695268_2093037760632848384_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com","username":"feminizm.daily"},"viewer_has_liked":false,"edge_liked_by":{"count":0}}},{"node":{"id":"17996979970143406","text":"Dobrze, \u017ce m\u00f3j ch\u0142opak jest normalny i podoba\u0142a mu si\u0119 reklama. Ja si\u0119 wzruszy\u0142am.","created_at":1547664265,"did_report_as_spam":false,"owner":{"id":"2130636700","is_verified":false,"profile_pic_url":"https://scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/525783ffa95aeef993422db653bbab9a/5D37D865/t51.2885-19/s150x150/16788555_200085113804539_2286338226987728896_a.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com","username":"ekocentryczka"},"viewer_has_liked":false,"edge_liked_by":{"count":2}}},{"node":{"id":"17961268729202003","text":"Ta reklama jest fantastyczna! \u0141zy w oczach i nadzieja na to, \u017ce czeka nas jednak zmiana na lepsze. Ma\u0142\u017conek popiera \ud83d\udc4c\ud83c\udffb","created_at":1547674430,"did_report_as_spam":false,"owner":{"id":"4527415927","is_verified":false,"profile_pic_url":"https://scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/04ebb5526859ccca57b710a16354301c/5D440FCD/t51.2885-19/s150x150/54277556_410544772856071_9151538786138587136_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-dus1-1.cdninstagram.com","username":"mistrzynicodziennosci"},"viewer_has_liked":false,"edge_liked_by":{"count":1}}},{"node":{"id":"17958294430217487","text":"@kawalek.nieba chcialabym dodac do twojego komentarza, ze jest jeszcze kwestia \"pink tax\". Fajnie jakby \"kobiece\" (czyli rozowe) kosmetyki i artykuly higieniczne kosztowaly tyle samo co ich \"meskie\" (czyli granatowe, niebieskie i czarne) odpowiedniki.","created_at